-- Merkel’s CDU, CSU Parties German Voter Support Falls, Bild Says
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2012-04-22T09:39:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-22/merkel-s-cdu-csu-parties-german-voter-support-falls-bild-says.html
Support for German Chancellor
 Angela Merkel ’s Christian Democratic Union and its Bavarian
sister party fell by one percentage point to 34 percent from the
week before, according to a weekly poll by  Bild am Sonntag .  The  Social Democratic Party  would attract 27 percent if
national elections were held today, the survey by Emnid for the
German newspaper showed. Support for the Green Party, the Pirate
Party and Free Democrats would be 13 percent, 12 percent and 4
percent, respectively. The Left Party would get 7 percent if an
election was held today, Bild said.  Emnid surveyed 2,768 people from April 12 to April 18.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
